Description
Hey guys, my name is Bekzodbek and i have created this " BIR KAMI TOLMAGAN DUNYO " project to document my learning process by turning the stuff I learn into tutorials and blog posts. I try to make my videos clear and easy to understand, but I want to point out that i am NOT an experienced developer, but rather a beginner that tries to learn by teaching. I only make a video about a topic, after i feel like I completely understand it. I try to not teach any outdated or wrong information and I research extensively, before I record a video. I also have a website where I write regular blog posts, but they are more about productivity and other stuff around programming and working in general. On this page you will also find the code to most of my videos, so i would be happy !!!
